uk.co.caprica.vlcj.player

Class MediaPlayerEventAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.co.caprica.vlcj.player.MediaPlayerEventAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MediaPlayerEventListener
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AudioMediaPlayerComponent, Condition

    public class MediaPlayerEventAdapter
extends Object
implements MediaPlayerEventListener
    Default implementation of the media player event listener.

    Simply override the methods you're interested in.

    Events are not raised on the Swing Event Dispatch thread so if updating user interface components in response to these events care must be taken to use SwingUtilities.invokeLater(Runnable).
